# Driver Registration & Dashboard System

## Description
This project allows drivers to register and view their info in a dashboard. It is built using a full-stack approach with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

## Setup

### Backend (Node.js)
1. Clone the repo.
2. Run `npm install` to install dependencies.
3. Run `node app.js` to start the backend server on port 5000.

### Frontend
1. Open `index.html` in a browser or deploy it on Vercel.

